<font color="#FF0000">BACK AND FORTH</font><br>
<tt>Fri Feb 21  4:13:52 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
I come here late at night when the wife and kids are in bed and the house is quiet. It's been 25 years since I left but I still go back EVERY DAY. Funny how a place draws you back, the smells on a warm night as the breeze blows or a sound and BANG your back, the smell of CS as you walk to the shower late at night or three kinds of music from three different directions. Helicopters do it, James Taylor tunes and the name Jane Fonda. The WALL must be a sight to see.<br>

